\)\)\(|\)\)\/\(2 | f' \((p)\) | \)\) \((\(|\)\(E\_k\)\(|\))\)\^2\)\)\)\)]],
  "  for  k  ",
  StyleBox["sufficiently large. \n",
    FontFamily->"Times New Roman"],
  StyleBox["\n",
    FontFamily->"Times New Roman",
